    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-8025-8094-d6975606311e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The framework starts by the outlining of principles that the ERS should follow and expands into how sticking to those principles can be put into practice. Experiments (backtested on MOOC data) show that their system makes recommendations in a more equal way with negligible loss of personalization.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
